<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Página Não Encontrada</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-primary: #f0f2f5;
            --text-primary: #1c1c1e;
            --text-secondary: #636366;
            --accent-primary: #4A6CFF;
            --accent-primary-rgb: 74, 108, 255;
            --ease-out-expo: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-primary);
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .ghost {
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            width: 150px;
            height: 180px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 100px 100px 0 0;
            position: relative;
            animation: float 3s var(--ease-out-expo) infinite;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .ghost-eyes {
            position: absolute;
            top: 60px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            display: flex;
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .ghost-eye {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background: var(--text-secondary);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .ghost-shadow {
            width: 100px;
            height: 15px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            animation: shadow-scale 3s var(--ease-out-expo) infinite;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-25px); }
        }

        @keyframes shadow-scale {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(0.85); }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
        }
        
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .btn-home {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent-primary);
            color: white;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s var(--ease-out-expo);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(var(--accent-primary-rgb), 0.2);
        }

        .btn-home:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(var(--accent-primary-rgb), 0.3);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="ghost-container">
            <div class="ghost">
                <div class="ghost-eyes">
                    <div class="ghost-eye"></div>
                    <div class="ghost-eye"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ghost-shadow"></div>
        </div>
        
        <h1>404</h1>
        <h2>Página Não Encontrada</h2>
        <p>A página que você está tentando acessar não existe ou foi movida. Que tal voltar para um lugar seguro?</p>
        <a href="/" class="btn-home">Voltar para a Página Inicial</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>